statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `anchong_goods_type` where MATCH(cid) AGAINST('3430') and added = 1
select `gid`, `title`, `price`, `sname`, `pic`, `vip_price`, `goods_id` from `anchong_goods_type` where MATCH(cid) AGAINST('3430') and added = 1 order by `created_at` desc limit 20 offset 0
